Pittsburgh Steelers
Davis was drafted by the Pittsburgh Steelers in the third round of the 2008 NFL Draft. After being drafted by the Steelers, he was converted to outside linebacker, though faced difficulty in the transition, as he was inactive for most of his rookie season. He was waived on September 4, 2009.
New England Patriots
Davis was signed to the New England Patriots practice squad on October 7, 2009.
